<task id="task-1241" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">#1 Activate Katalon Studio</title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><context class="- topic/section task/context ">When you first open  the <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/> application, you are prompted to activate the 30-day trial for <ph conkeyref="name-variables/kse-abbreviation" class="- topic/ph "/>,  for <ph conkeyref="name-variables/kre-abbreviation" class="- topic/ph "/> - an add-on for console execution, and for <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-testcloud" class="- topic/ph "/> - a cloud-based testing environment. <p class="- topic/p ">You can start using <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/> after activating. Follow these steps:</p></context><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Launch the <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/> application.</cmd><stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Katalon Studio Activation</uicontrol> dialog displays as below. Sign in to your Katalon account to activate your license.<p class="- topic/p "><image width="500" href="../../Katalon_Studio_Installation/Install_Katalon_Studio_on_macOS_and_Windows/Images/ks-850-se-activation.png" class="- topic/image "/></p></stepresult></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">After you are done, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Activate</uicontrol>.</cmd></step></steps><result class="- topic/section task/result "><ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/> is ready for use.</result></taskbody></task>